356	Macaroni Salad	\N	Cooked and rinsed pasta\n1 cup cut carrots\n½ cup cut celery\n½ cup chopped green onion\n1 cup parsley\n½ cup peppadew peppers\n½ tsp garlic powder\n1 pinch kosher salt\n1 pinch freshly ground pepper\nTwo spoonfuls mayonnaise\n1 spoonful sour cream\n1 Tbsp Dijon mustard	Cook and rinse chosen pasta.\nIn a mixing bowl, add cut carrots, celery, green onion, parsley, peppadew peppers, garlic powder, a pinch of salt, ground pepper, and toss together.\nAdd 2 spoonfuls of mayonnaise to pasta.\nAdd 1 spoonful of sour cream.\nAdd 1 Tbsp of Dijon mustard to pasta.\nFill half a plate with your home fries and the other half with your fresh pasta salad. Continue on to make toppings!	garbageplate
